Wood Green animal charity has teamed up with cleaning and DIY app Handy to offer a cat fostering service . 
  Cats will not just catch mice but the scent they leave behind can discourage rodents from returning . 
  The charity says the presence of a cat and the scent it leaves can scare away unwanted rodents . 
  Those looking to borrow a cat to help rid their homes of mouse infestation are asked to be 'flexible, patient and caring towards the animals'